  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Genjutsu (Phantasm)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 9 (Spell Level 5)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 12</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 24 | <b>Successes:</b> 4</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 12 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 26</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, Mob</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>This technique allows you to erase your presence from the target's senses and create eight illusory replicas that attack the target from all sides. Make a melee attack against the target. If the subject failed its save, the attack gains a +10 bonus to the attack roll, Kawarimi Defense 3, and the subject loses its Dexterity bonus to Defense against the attack.<br><br>If you can use the Shiden technique (p226), you may increase the Chakra Cost by 6 and increase the Perform Requirements by 4 to allow this technique to be used from 30 ft. away, adding the same conditions and effects of Shiden to the attack.<br><br>This technique counts as a Rank 12 genjutsu technique for the purpose of identifying it.</p>\n\n\n\n",
